summary: This is a calendar entry for a canceled FBI interview with David Rodgers, scheduled for February 7, 2020, in the Southern District of New York. It indicates an investigative activity related to the Epstein case that did not occur as planned.

keyFacts: The FBI in New York scheduled an interview with David Rodgers for February 7, 2020.
